Programs the vendor ID of the USB-DUX fast board into its EEPROM
----------------------------------------------------------------

This needs to be done once so that the USB-DUX fast driver can
auto-detect the board.

Prerequisite: 
as31 (standard Ubuntu package)

Build: 
Just type "make".

Usage:
fxload -2 prog_id.hex
or add the "99-usbduxfirmware.rules" to "/etc/udev/rules.d/"
